From CARTER EDWARD A Subject Re DoD Oficial tm Newbie Bike of Choice In article John Daker writes I propose that the Official DoD Newbie Bike of Choice tm be the ZX Nothing like giving newbies a land rocket to practice It offers enough power so that a novice rider can safely accelerate out of harms way in situations where a more experienced rider would use complex avoidance Accelerate right into the back of an wheel How's the easiest way to get newbies of the road Regards University of Toronto Computer Engineering PowerUsersGroupChairman ' I'm taking a ride with my best DoD